title: Sister Driller
description:
Poor Takehiro-kun: he's cursed with a younger sister who is a). cute, b). manipulative and c). very selfish. She knows her older brother finds her adorable and uses it ruthlessly to make him do her every bidding. But Takehiro-kun has a secret. He knows his little sister wants his attention so badly, she'll do anything to keep her hold over him....
